{"tid":118506,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲清水富美加出家引退各電視台報導","createTime":"2017-02-13T05:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T11:21:39.000Z","uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"298b83cab1f1c2c554f6c8e434064b919699d532","tid":118506,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/okvhpwjz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fokvhpwjz&h=b3355c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年22歲的日本電影《變態超人》女星清水富美加，昨日突然宣佈出家引退，事件轟動日本演藝圈。<br />\n富美加於2008年入行，是新垣結衣、吉川日奈等的同門師妹，近年受到事務所力捧，今年她原定有三部電影上映，當中包括真人版《東京喰種》，但她因篤信「幸福科學」宗教而決定退出演藝界，其法號「千眼美子」。富美加本月4日以身體不適為由向公司請假，上月更找律師向事務所請辭，同時把Twitter賬戶刪除。「幸福科學」是當地新興宗教，在港約有千名信徒，昨日「幸福科學」舉行記者會，指富美加出家是因為不滿演藝界的奴隸合約，同時又透露富美加多次向身邊人表示想死。富美加雖缺席記者會，但公開親筆聲明表示想過安定的生活<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0ByVnvVWKY6FdWHlJalJsbDFXVDQ/view?usp=sharing \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0ByVnvVWKY6FdWHlJalJsbDFXVDQ%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%20&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=f123674c\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0ByVnvVWKY6FdWHlJalJsbDFXVDQ/view?usp=sharing </a><br />\n日テレ報導<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0ByVnvVWKY6FdNVhzdEVBWDlFajQ/view?usp=sharing \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0ByVnvVWKY6FdNVhzdEVBWDlFajQ%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%20&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=e2e2f7ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0ByVnvVWKY6FdNVhzdEVBWDlFajQ/view?usp=sharing </a><br />\n朝日報導<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0ByVnvVWKY6FdcENFY3NuQ3RWeUE/view?usp=sharing \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0ByVnvVWKY6FdcENFY3NuQ3RWeUE%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing%20&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=b042f6af\" target=\"_bla